in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.complexbrot

Class ComplexBrotFractalGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.FractalGenerator
      • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.PixelFractalGenerator
        • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.complexbrot.ComplexBrotFractalGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pannable, Zoomable, java.io.Serializable 

    public class ComplexBrotFractalGenerator
extends PixelFractalGenerator
    ComplexBrot fractal generator NOTE: Only supports the *BROT (excepting MANDELBROT, of course) fractal modes. Other modes will throw an UnsupportedOperationException
    See Also:
    ComplexFractalGenerator, ComplexBrotFractalParams, Serialized Form
